00:00:06.890 --> 00:00:12.620
Beauty, Strength and Transparency in Business;
that is DIAMOND GROUP of Industries.

00:00:12.620 --> 00:00:18.730
Diamonds are the stones that roll over to
make the impossible -- possible; with perfection...

00:00:18.730 --> 00:00:20.170
this perfection is called 'Diamond'.

00:00:20.170 --> 00:00:23.869
They are here to provide essentials to bring
happiness in your life.

00:00:23.869 --> 00:00:27.539
The Diamonds Group- is in the business of
Food Processing, Steel and Garment.

00:00:27.539 --> 00:00:37.010
The Diamond Roller Flour Mills Private Limited
is the wheat processing unit situated at Kottayam,

00:00:37.010 --> 00:00:38.010
Kerala.

00:00:38.010 --> 00:00:40.120
Here quality wheat products such as Maida,
Atta and Sooji are produced.

00:00:40.120 --> 00:00:43.960
These are used in Hotels, Bakeries and households
in the making Bread, Biscuits, Cakes, Kuboos,

00:00:43.960 --> 00:00:45.170
Paratha, Chapathi and Halwai.

00:00:45.170 --> 00:00:51.969
As we enter, we would witness many small things
which are addressed to its perfection by the

00:00:51.969 --> 00:00:53.030
mill.

00:00:53.030 --> 00:01:02.379
Clean and hygienically built and maintained
mill building and warehouses ensures utmost

00:01:02.379 --> 00:01:03.379
hygienic products.

00:01:03.379 --> 00:01:05.340
The water requirement is met from Rainwater
Harvesting and modern filtration and treatment

00:01:05.340 --> 00:01:08.330
system .This ensures that the water used for
the food industry complies with Food Safety

00:01:08.330 --> 00:01:09.330
Standards.

00:01:09.330 --> 00:01:13.291
Since wheat is not grown in the southern part
of India, the mill initiated the process of

00:01:13.291 --> 00:01:17.479
building 12000 Metric Tonne of Steel silo
storage to ensure continuous supply of quality

00:01:17.479 --> 00:01:18.479
raw material.

00:01:18.479 --> 00:01:21.659
This project is designed and supplied by Buhler
AG, Switzerland and GSI, USA.

00:01:21.659 --> 00:01:23.930
The beauty of quality... the importance of
customer relationship... the assurance of

00:01:23.930 --> 00:01:25.020
offering the best products...

00:01:25.020 --> 00:01:27.399
These are the three things that 'Diamond'
believes in.

00:01:27.399 --> 00:01:29.570
They always offer quality products without
any compromise.

00:01:29.570 --> 00:01:33.369
This is their strength and with the support
of their esteemed customers Diamond Roller

00:01:33.369 --> 00:01:35.049
Flour Mills has been successful for the last
21 years.

00:01:35.049 --> 00:01:41.090
In the year 2011, Diamond signed a contract
with Buhler AG, Switzerland, a world leader

00:01:41.090 --> 00:01:45.729
in building flour mills to put up a state-
of- the- art plant with a capacity 275 Metric

00:01:45.729 --> 00:01:46.729
Tonne per Day.

00:01:46.729 --> 00:01:50.260
This was the first flour mill in India to
import the new generation equipment entirely

00:01:50.260 --> 00:01:51.260
from Europe.

00:01:51.260 --> 00:01:54.300
The plant was commissioned in February 2013
and from then onwards is producing top notch

00:01:54.300 --> 00:01:55.631
products in the state of Kerala.

00:01:55.631 --> 00:01:59.430
The advanced machines from Europe are made
of food safe materials and also made to meet

00:01:59.430 --> 00:02:00.930
the stringent European Union norms in food
safety and traceability.

00:02:00.930 --> 00:02:04.090
The complete plant is run on Wincos software
provided by Buhler using Siemens PLC.

00:02:04.090 --> 00:02:07.159
Carefully selected wheat grains are blended
and thoroughly cleaned to remove all inherent

00:02:07.159 --> 00:02:11.250
impurities before milling them in to various
end products like Maida, Semolina, Atta and

00:02:11.250 --> 00:02:12.250
Bran.

00:02:12.250 --> 00:02:14.660
At each stage of the process, samples are
drawn and checked for quality before packing

00:02:14.660 --> 00:02:15.819
in food safe bags.

00:02:15.819 --> 00:02:17.500
The by-product Bran goes to cattle feed industry.

00:02:17.500 --> 00:02:20.910
The entire air from the plant is discharged
into the atmosphere after going through high

00:02:20.910 --> 00:02:23.810
quality air jet filters to ensure no emission
in to environment.

00:02:23.810 --> 00:02:49.190
Starting from wheat receipt to final product
packing is completely automated in such a

00:02:49.190 --> 00:03:06.060
way that the products are of highest quality
and are untouched by human hands during the

00:03:06.060 --> 00:03:07.470
whole production process.

00:03:07.470 --> 00:03:16.430
Fully trained and qualified persons at each
stage of process ensure utmost purity and

00:03:16.430 --> 00:03:17.430
quality are delivered.

00:03:17.430 --> 00:03:19.480
Fully equipped laboratory compliments the
state of the art production process plant

00:03:19.480 --> 00:03:32.270
in delivering pure and safe food to customers.

00:03:32.270 --> 00:03:44.400
Clean and attractive packing in food grade
HDPE laminated bags ensures safe product.

00:03:44.400 --> 00:03:53.730
Products are packed in bags after printing
the date of manufacture and batch to ensure

00:03:53.730 --> 00:04:00.209
easy identification for dispatching it to
customers on first-cum-first basis.

00:04:00.209 --> 00:04:09.420
This also helps to get feedback from esteemed
customers on quality.

00:04:09.420 --> 00:04:26.770
Diamond is one of the first flour mills that
is certified for the Food Safety Management

00:04:26.770 --> 00:04:29.310
system under FSSC 22000-2011 by DNV.

